{
  "stem": "304.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then she remarried a yeshiva bocher.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she had seven more children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And even though it was a very rich family, there was always a difference in the children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Especially by my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Her children, our children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she felt that she grew up with a real-- this is how heard always the stories with grandfather-- I always say like in a-- the stories-- in the old-fashioned stories when you describe a-- a-- a step-father or step-mother.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She was only two years old when she lost her father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She hardly remembered him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And when she married-- when I go back, I was in my grandparents' house, I remember once when my grandmother was still alive, and we figured out, I was probably three or four years old, and I went to her at Shabbat morning.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this is the picture I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Nothing else about this grandmother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She was in a wheelchair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She suffered from a very serious arthritis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So she was in a wheelchair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she wheeled herself to the credenz and opened it and took out some cake and gave me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This was customary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "When grandchild came, she gave me cake.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That's what I remember from my maternal grandmother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then when she died, my step-grandfather remarried and had another child with this woman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And something happened in the family, because we never went there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were not in speaking terms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I think what happened, that my father-- after he married my mother and years later-- he realized it was such a rich home-- even though they were 11 children.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "That when my grandmother died, she wanted her inheritance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And it was a-- a-- quite an amount, because otherwise I don't think they would have gone-- they went to court with it.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
